{"tid":2114261,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港區國安法：多間美加VPN公司關閉香港伺服器","createTime":"2020-07-18T16:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T03:01:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ab7d22574c0279739f446ca138dd52a878fd8607","tid":2114261,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T16:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/obipYx5sDeONUcwvaMm3iQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-07/ec0c1790-c891-11ea-8dff-13a9b7691d08\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FobipYx5sDeONUcwvaMm3iQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-07%2Fec0c1790-c891-11ea-8dff-13a9b7691d08&h=a65c7899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港《港區國安法》實施後，多間互聯網巨企表明暫時拒絕香港政府索取用戶資料的請求。美國消費者新聞與商業頻道周五（17日）報道，外國多間提供虛擬私人網絡（VPN）服務公司，亦已或正考慮關閉在港的伺服器。中國國務院港澳事務辦公室暫未回應。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，總部設在美國的IPVanish周三（15日）在網上表示，為保障香港用戶的自由，已關閉在港的VPN伺服器並暫停營運。IPVanish形容香港一度是網絡自由的堡壘，現在受到與中國相同程度的互聯網限制，「不幸地要將香港及中國視為一體」。<br />\n<br />\n除IPVanish外，加拿大的TunnelBear周一（13日）亦提到，或關閉香港的伺服器，又指《港區國安法》引發廣泛憂慮，損害香港的言論自由。至於英屬維爾京群島公司Surfshark則稱，公司的VPN伺服器沒有儲存任何用戶資料，因此不會關閉在港的伺服器。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/港區國安法多間美加vpn公司關閉香港伺服器-010004476.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E5%A4%9A%E9%96%93%E7%BE%8E%E5%8A%A0vpn%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BC%BA%E6%9C%8D%E5%99%A8-010004476.html&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeBz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=3afe4a01\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/港區國安法多間美加vpn公司關閉香港伺服器-010004476.html</a>"},{"pid":"fae3162de24e38d6374ea52a1720cbfd3e853b97","tid":2114261,"uid":231583,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T16:31:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已